{{Quote|I'll summon room service. Marinated range-squab for four, and a few magnums of chilled T'iil-T'iil?|Han Solo to Hasti Troujow, held in captivity by the Survivors|<ref name="legacy">''[[Han Solo and the Lost Legacy]]''</ref>}}
'''T'iil-T'iil''' was an expensive [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage that was produced and exported from a location near the [[Moss Caverns]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Loj]]. It was notable for the triple carbonation and filtering process used in its creation.<ref name="swg">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=item|T'illa-T'iil}}</ref>

